net.pandoragames.far.ui.model

Enum OperationType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OperationType>
      • net.pandoragames.far.ui.model.OperationType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<OperationType>

    public enum OperationType
extends java.lang.Enum<OperationType>
    Represents an operation like "find" or "replace". Each page (or tab) in FAR is dedicated to a particular operation, e.g. "find" or "replace". This enum serves to identify those operations in varying contexts.
    Author:
    Olivier Wehner
    See Also:
    OperationForm
